{"tid":619275,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解啲人咁憎皮草？","createTime":"2018-04-06T13:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T13:46:42.000Z","uid":132859,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db9168bafbea3274d8cfff1dfbf3e1506027b405","tid":619275,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"成日去啲講皮草嘅post都見到成班人留言話著皮草係動物殺手，著住動物啲皮好嘔心咁 <br />\n<br />\n但係雖然養殖皮草嘅農莊的確比人爆過有虐待動物嘅情況 <br />\n但係普通養殖食用肉類嘅農場都同樣有呢啲情況<br />\n<br />\n點解啲人憎皮草多過憎食肉同埋用皮革呢？ <br />\n明明一件皮草買咗可以著幾十年但係肉就要日日食<br />\n殺動物做糧食傷害過嘅動物絕對比買皮草嘅傷害動物多幾百倍幾千倍<br />\n<br />\n點解連肉食者都會咁憎皮草呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果改革皮草養殖農場嘅不道德養殖行為,啲人又會唔會鍾意返人著皮草呢？"},{"pid":"61df902f370e9667bc76a6c95c7ffb424341ae66","tid":619275,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:38:44.000Z","msg":"做皮草的動物除左塊皮有價值，其他部分有咩用 ?"},{"pid":"f1cdaf6a4975bf82b399c108d45651c0350cabbb","tid":619275,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"肉食不可缺，皮草為保暖太多物料可取代"},{"pid":"bfba2137d39bd62434ef62b7f3efcbffa3ebc61b","tid":619275,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cdaf6a4975bf82b399c108d45651c0350cabbb","tid":619275,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"肉食不可缺，皮草為保暖太多物料可取代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"265ae1077c1666b2af1b512e58109bbdf4f418a6","tid":619275,"uid":81197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1cdaf6a4975bf82b399c108d45651c0350cabbb","tid":619275,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"肉食不可缺，皮草為保暖太多物料可取代"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:43:26.000Z","msg":"咁皮草個luxury feel夠不可取代"},{"pid":"0e00993e99e66073bf7b637c4e3b289a37fef8d8","tid":619275,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265ae1077c1666b2af1b512e58109bbdf4f41